    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PETRO指责哥伦比亚中央银行试图破坏增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/petro-accuses-colombia-central-bank-of-trying-to-sabotage-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗（Gustavo Petro）袭击了中央银行，并指控该银行在董事会在3月的政策会议上挑战较低的利率之后，试图伤害经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/petro-accuses-colombia-central-bank-of-trying-to-sabotage-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 20:45:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普以票务剥头，新的行政命令费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-to-target-ticket-scalping-fees-with-new-executive-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统将在周一签署一项行政命令，旨在打破票务和费用，以增加参加消费者现场活动的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-to-target-ticket-scalping-fees-with-new-executive-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 20:42:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普起诉他对公民身份证明的投票要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-sued-over-order-to-require-proof-of-citizenship-to-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的行政命令指导美国选民注册的重大变更以及如何计算邮寄选票，这是在代表拉丁美洲人，军人家庭和大学生的非营利组织中被挑战为违宪的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-sued-over-order-to-require-proof-of-citizenship-to-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 20:36:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈佛警告特朗普，有90亿美元的风险资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-administration-to-review-billions-in-grants-to-harvard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府将审查大约90亿美元的联邦合同和给哈佛大学的赠款，扩大对校园反犹太主义的调查，这也针对哥伦比亚大学的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-administration-to-review-billions-in-grants-to-harvard</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 19:48:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
